Class SeasonView

java.lang.Object
Screen
SeasonView
public class SeasonView
extends Screen
Season View is a GUI implementation where the user can see how their garden would look in different seasons such as SUMMER, WINTER, FALL

Author:
Malachi Parks

  • Method Details

    • showScreen

      public void showScreen()
      Upon start, if the screen isn't show the method will pull in the users preferred season and set it to the startingSeason. Then will set shown to true. Removes the gridpane and redraws it using the drawGrid method in view. Reanchors the grid pane over the rectangle then adds it to the scene and shows the scene.
      Overrides:
      showScreen in class Screen
